column2: Independent and capable of self-organization. Potentially self-centered, with a strong desire for self-expression.
Receptive to other people and sensitive to the undercurrents involved in relationships.
An objective, rather than personal, outlook on relationships. A desire for a public role and to participate in society.
A drive to make a mark on the world. This can be beneficial, but may become disruptive when overly attached to an ideal.
